# Regression: multi-overload dispatch inside a match-arm body must
# propagate branches the same way it does at the top level. Companion
# to multi_overload_in_if.msh — `checkMatchBlock` had the same
# single-state walk pattern as the old `checkIfBlock`.

def f ({v} --)
    seen!
    @seen match
        dict :
            @seen "x" in not if
                "found" wl
            end
        ,
        _ : ,
    end
end
